{"type": "article", "id": 2748, "title": "Berimbau 灯具", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-10T08:04:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232518jRbYvw1DceS6gAZ2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计工作室 Atelier Bam 日前为巴西传统设计品牌 Bertolucci 设计了一系列名为“ Berimbau ”的灯具，既可以当作桌灯，亦可以作为吊灯或立灯使用。这一系列的灯饰由三个主要部分组成：反射镜，带牙槽的电线以及灯具。用户如要旋转反射镜，只需要拉一下灯具，将它移向你希望的方向。“我们想让用户可以全方位控制灯源。”设计师说。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232516bXuS2yv6JAmChGiY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232516L4Ekscv7UqAt3g1J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232517685YqLXRuaSf7Qid.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232517gKJkfRohDu0vXsE4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232517vnpbIUQTNPsDqfJO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}